name: .MLMODEL
summary: Learn about .MLMODEL files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

instructions: You can open an MLMODEL file in Apple Xcode (Mac). Doing so allows you to view the MLMODEL's metadata and preview the model's prediction capabilities. If you have Xcode installed, you can open your MLMODEL file by double-clicking the file.
